                        android:maxLines="4"
                        android:scrollHorizontally="false"
                        android:text="Hi, my name is Wu QiHui and I am a student in SIT currently studying in Information Security. \nI like coding, especially in python, and creating user friendly applications. Hope that you will like this application that we made! :>"
